unnormalised: Bhau, maka matshem zata kai mhunn dista, vo VS Code-antle debugging chodd koshthishta zait asa? Mhaka 3 voram laglim mhozo Python script kiteak barebhari cholona mhunn sodunk; 27 linier mhaka syntax error aslem. Kiteak IntelliJ borem ashem dista? Mhozo ixtt Rohan tannem shapath gheun sangta, Rs. 20,000 license-ak borem mhunn. Konnankui anik hem dukhtem ashem zata kai? Vo mhaka 3:00 AM-ak chodd coding korchea karnan zata kai?
